{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14134/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14134"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:41:34"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman whispers in a man's ear as another woman approaches."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14134","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14134"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1/44f8b017-1a4a-4d33-b83b-1cf13336a11b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T15:05:58.617Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>As Alma whispers in Reynolds’s ear “have fun with your next opponent,” she leans down, very literally stooping to his level. He lashed out from jealousy over Dr. Hardy, ultimately sending her away from the table. Here, she invokes the same anxieties. Like his previous comment about not cheating, her comment is ostensibly about the backgammon game but ultimately speaks more to other issues in their relationship, including his history of taking on lovers and muses and unceremoniously dumping them when he feels ready to move on.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14134/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:264.93506493506476,334.2857142857142,787.0129870129871,636.6233766233765"}}}]}]}]}